         <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">

<ab><lb n="1"/> <w lemma="θεά">θεᾷ</w> <persName type="divine"><name nymRef="#Ἀφροδίτη">Ἀφροδείτῃ</name></persName> <g ref="#star"/> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <persName type="emperor"><w lemma="αὐτοκράτωρ">Αὐτοκράτορι</w> <name nymRef="#Καῖσαρ">Καίσαρι</name> <w lemma="θεός">θεοῦ</w> <name nymRef="#Τραιανός">Τραϊανοῦ</name> <w lemma="υἱός">υἱῷ</w> <w lemma="θεός">θεοῦ</w> <name nymRef="#Νέρβα">Νέρβα</name> <lb n="2"/><w lemma="υἱωνός"><supplied reason="lost">υἱ</supplied>ωνῷ</w> <name nymRef="#Τραιανός">Τραϊανῷ</name> <name nymRef="#Ἁδριανός">Ἁδριανῷ</name> <w lemma="σεβαστός">Σεβαστῷ</w></persName><w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τῷ</w> <w lemma="δῆμος">δήμῳ</w> <g ref="#star"/> <persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Περίτας">Περείτας</name> <name nymRef="#Ζήνων">Ζήνωνος</name> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w> <name nymRef="#Ζήνων">Ζήνωνος</name> <lb n="3"/><space extent="3" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/> <name nymRef="#Ἄτταλος">Ἄτταλος</name></persName> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸ</w> <w lemma="περιφλίωμα">περιφλίωμα</w> <g ref="#hole"/> <w>ἐκ<sic n="superfluous">κ</sic></w> <w lemma="ὁ">τῶν</w><w lemma="ἴδιος"> ἰδίων</w> <space extent="1" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/> <w lemma="ἀνατίθημι">ἀνέθηκεν</w> <g ref="#scroll"/> </ab>
</div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>The cutter had to avoid a hole in l. 3.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the goddess Aphrodite, to the Imperator Hadrian Augustus son of the god Trajan, grandson of the god Nerva, to the People: Pereitas Attalos son of Zenon the son of Zenon dedicated the <seg cert="low">decoration</seg> of the doorway at his own expense.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The same text was inscribed on the north-east doorway (<ref type="inscription" n="1558" target="050208.xml"/> =Mendel, 168b) with differences in layout and a different hand.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="bibliography">
            <p>Published by <bibl n="mendel1906">Mendel, CRAI 1906, <citedRange>168a</citedRange> note 1</bibl>, whence <bibl n="PHI">
                  <author>McCabe</author>
                  <title level="m">PHI Aphrodisias</title>
                  <citedRange n="256990">112</citedRange>
               </bibl>; mentioned by <bibl n="wilhelm1933">Wilhelm, <title>Jahreshefte</title> 1933, 55-61, 56</bibl>.</p>
         </div>
